OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey start across the region
OL,6,Fwith outbreaks of drizzle. A spells of
OL,7,Fheavy rain with blustery winds will
OL,8,Fmove through in the afternoon, with
OL,9,Fbrighter skies following and a few
OL,10,Fheavy showers.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBreezy tonight with clear
OL,13,Fspells and occasional showers moving
OL,14,Fthrough, which could be heavy at
OL,15,Ftimes. Staying mild with the brisk
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
