OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FSunny spells and scattered
OL,6,Fshowers on Thursday. Turning
OL,7,Fincreasingly cloudy through the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Feeling pleasant in any
OL,9,Fbrighter spells.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA spell
OL,12,Fof rain will move through on Friday.
OL,13,FScattered showers on Saturday. Most
OL,14,Flikely turning dry, warm and sunny on
OL,15,FSunday.
